<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>English Zone — خطة حملة مايو 2026</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@300;400;600;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --red: #E24B4A;
    --red-dark: #A32D2D;
    --red-light: #FCEBEB;
    --amber: #EF9F27;
    --amber-light: #FAEEDA;
    --amber-dark: #854F0B;
    --green: #3B6D11;
    --green-light: #EAF3DE;
    --blue: #185FA5;
    --blue-light: #E6F1FB;
    --pink: #993556;
    --pink-light: #FBEAF0;
    --dark: #1a1a18;
    --dark2: #2C2C2A;
    --mid: #5F5E5A;
    --light: #F1EFE8;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --border: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    --shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    --shadow-lg: 0 12px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    --radius: 12px;
    --radius-sm: 8px;
    --font: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: var(--font);
    background: #f8f6f1;
    color: var(--dark);
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  header {
    background: var(--dark);
    padding: 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .header-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 50%, rgba(226,75,74,0.25) 0%, transparent 60%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(239,159,39,0.15) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }
  .header-inner {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 2rem 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .header-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(226,75,74,0.2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(226,75,74,0.4);
    color: #ff8a89;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .header-badge::before { content: '●'; font-size: 8px; animation: pulse 1.5s infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:0.3} }

  header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }
  header h1 span { color: var(--red); }
  header p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .header-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .hstat {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hstat-num { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 900; color: #fff; }
  .hstat-label { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top: 2px; }

  /* ── NAV TABS ── */
  .nav-wrap {
    background: var(--white);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .nav-inner {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  .nav-inner::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .nav-tab {
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--mid);
    background: none;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-tab:hover { color: var(--dark); }
  .nav-tab.active { color: var(--red); border-bottom-color: var(--red); }

  /* ── MAIN ── */
  main {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .tab-panel { display: none; }
  .tab-panel.active { display: block; }

  /* ── SECTION TITLE ── */
  .sec-title {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--red);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .sec-title::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); }

  /* ── CARDS ── */
  .card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .card-sm { padding: 1rem 1.25rem; }

  /* ── GRID ── */
  .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
  .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
  .grid-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
  .mb1 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .mb2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .mb3 { margin-bottom: 2rem; }

  /* ── BADGE ── */
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-left: 4px;
  }
  .b-red { background: var(--red-light); color: var(--red-dark); }
  .b-amber { background: var(--amber-light); color: var(--amber-dark); }
  .b-green { background: var(--green-light); color: var(--green); }
  .b-blue { background: var(--blue-light); color: var(--blue); }
  .b-pink { background: var(--pink-light); color: var(--pink); }

  /* ══════════════════════════
     BIG IDEA
  ══════════════════════════ */
  .bigidea-hero {
    background: var(--dark);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .bigidea-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -80px; left: -80px;
    width: 300px; height: 300px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(226,75,74,0.3), transparent 70%);
  }
  .bigidea-hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -60px; right: -40px;
    width: 250px; height: 250px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(239,159,39,0.2), transparent 70%);
  }
  .bigidea-hero h2 {
    position: relative;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 4vw, 38px);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .bigidea-hero h2 span { color: var(--red); }
  .bigidea-hero p {
    position: relative;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .pillar-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.25rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .pillar-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); }
  .pillar-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .pillar-card h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .pillar-card p { font-size: 12px; color: var(--mid); line-height: 1.7; }

  .audience-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .audience-row:hover { border-color: var(--red); }
  .aud-num {
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--red);
    color: #fff;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .aud-num.n2 { background: var(--amber); }
  .aud-num.n3 { background: var(--blue); }
  .aud-num.n4 { background: var(--green); }
  .aud-info h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .aud-info p { font-size: 12px; color: var(--mid); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ══════════════════════════
     SCRIPTS
  ══════════════════════════ */
  .script-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .script-head {
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--dark);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .script-num {
    width: 44px; height: 44px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--red);
    color: #fff;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px; font-weight: 900;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .script-head h3 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .script-head p { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); }

  .scene-wrap { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .scene {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--light);
  }
  .scene:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .scene-tag {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 72px;
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    padding-top: 4px;
  }
  .st-hook { color: var(--red); }
  .st-setup { color: var(--blue); }
  .st-pain { color: #993C1D; }
  .st-break { color: var(--red-dark); }
  .st-bridge { color: var(--amber-dark); }
  .st-solution { color: var(--green); }
  .st-cta { color: var(--red); }
  .scene-body { font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--dark2); line-height: 1.9; }
  .scene-body strong { font-weight: 700; }
  .scene-body .dir {
    display: block;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--mid);
    background: var(--light);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin: 6px 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .scene-body .screen-text {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--dark);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin: 6px 0;
  }
  .scene-body .cta-final {
    background: var(--red);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-align: center;
    display: block;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════
     CALENDAR
  ══════════════════════════ */
  .cal-legend {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .cal-legend span {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .cal-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(150px, 1fr));
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .cal-item {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 12px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .cal-item:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: var(--shadow); border-color: currentColor; }
  .cal-item .day-n {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--mid);
    margin-bottom: 5px;
    display: block;
  }
  .cal-item .day-t {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .day-pill {
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700;
    padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .dp-video { background: var(--red-light); color: var(--red); }
  .dp-story { background: var(--amber-light); color: var(--amber-dark); }
  .dp-post  { background: var(--blue-light); color: var(--blue); }
  .dp-ad    { background: var(--green-light); color: var(--green); }
  .dp-reel  { background: var(--pink-light); color: var(--pink); }

  .cal-item.cv { border-top: 3px solid var(--red); }
  .cal-item.cs { border-top: 3px solid var(--amber); }
  .cal-item.cp { border-top: 3px solid var(--blue); }
  .cal-item.ca { border-top: 3px solid var(--green); }
  .cal-item.cr { border-top: 3px solid var(--pink); }

  /* ══════════════════════════
     ADS
  ══════════════════════════ */
  .budget-row {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .budget-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .budget-meta span { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); }
  .budget-meta em { font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; color: var(--mid); }
  .budget-track {
    height: 10px;
    background: var(--light);
    border-radius: 5px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .budget-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 5px;
    transition: width 1s ease;
  }

  .platform-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.25rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .platform-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); }
  .platform-icon {
    width: 40px; height: 40px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .platform-card h4 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .platform-card .role { font-size: 12px; color: var(--mid); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .platform-card ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
  .platform-card ul li {
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--dark2);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
  }
  .platform-card ul li::before { content: '›'; color: var(--red); font-weight: 700; }

  .funnel-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 1.25rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .funnel-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .funnel-num {
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .fn1 { background: var(--red-light); color: var(--red); }
  .fn2 { background: var(--amber-light); color: var(--amber-dark); }
  .fn3 { background: var(--green-light); color: var(--green); }
  .fn4 { background: var(--blue-light); color: var(--blue); }
  .funnel-item h4 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .funnel-item p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--mid); line-height: 1.7; }

  .rt-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 12px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--light);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .rt-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .rt-day {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--red);
    width: 70px;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }
  .rt-text { font-size: 13px; color: var(--dark2); line-height: 1.7; }
  .rt-text strong { font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); }

  /* ══════════════════════════
     HOOKS
  ══════════════════════════ */
  .hooks-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .hook-item {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .hook-item:hover { border-color: var(--red); box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
  .hook-item:hover .hook-num { background: var(--red); color: #fff; }
  .hook-top { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .hook-num {
    width: 28px; height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--light);
    color: var(--mid);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .hook-cat { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--mid); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .hook-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--dark); line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 500; }

  /* ══════════════════════════
     KPIs
  ══════════════════════════ */
  .kpi-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .kpi-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); transform: translateY(-3px); }
  .kpi-card .kpi-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .kpi-card .kpi-num {
    font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--dark);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .kpi-card .kpi-num span { color: var(--red); }
  .kpi-card .kpi-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--mid); line-height: 1.5; }

  .metric-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 12px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--light);
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .metric-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .metric-name { font-size: 13px; color: var(--dark); }
  .metric-target { flex-shrink: 0; }

  .week-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--light);
  }
  .week-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .week-num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--red);
    width: 75px;
    padding-top: 3px;
  }
  .week-content h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .week-content p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--mid); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: var(--dark);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  footer strong { color: var(--red); }

  /* ── PRINT ── */
  @media print {
    .nav-wrap { position: static; }
    .tab-panel { display: block !important; page-break-before: always; }
    .tab-panel:first-child { page-break-before: auto; }
  }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    main { padding: 1rem; }
    .header-inner { padding: 2rem 1rem; }
    .script-head { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .cal-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(130px, 1fr)); }
  }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .tab-panel.active > * {
    animation: fadeUp 0.3s ease both;
  }
  .tab-panel.active > *:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
  .tab-panel.active > *:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.10s; }
  .tab-panel.active > *:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header>
  <div class="header-bg"></div>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="header-badge">English Zone · خطة مايو 2026</div>
    <h1>احنا مش بندرّس...<br><span>بنخليك تعيش اللغة</span></h1>
    <p>خطة تسويقية متكاملة لشهر مايو — قائمة على الإيموشن والألم الحقيقي. هدفها الأول: أكبر عدد تسجيلات.</p>
    <div class="header-stats">
      <div class="hstat"><div class="hstat-num">30</div><div class="hstat-label">يوم محتوى مخطط</div></div>
